profile.bio: Partner @GoogleVentures.  Investor in @SlackHQ, @CoreOSLinux, @Jet. Seeking data-driven approaches and rapid innovation. Grew/led ops @KivaSystems, @Amazon. Dad of 2, married to @AllisonMuni.
